      • copyWeightsToModel

        public static Model copyWeightsToModel(Model model,
                                       java.util.Map<java.lang.String,KerasLayer> kerasLayers)
                                throws InvalidKerasConfigurationException
        Helper function to import weights from nested Map into existing model. Depends critically on matched layer and parameter names. In general this seems to be straightforward for most Keras models and layersOrdered, but there may be edge cases.
        Parameters:
        model - DL4J Model interface
        Returns:
        DL4J Model interface
        Throws:
        InvalidKerasConfigurationException - Invalid Keras config
